        "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Troubleshoot and resolve Zoom meeting link issues for Surge AI and Growth X weekly sync.](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2879.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [Persistent Zoom link access problems despite multiple attempts](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2884.0)\n  - [Issue likely stems from calendar integration or Zoom account settings](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2889.0)\n  - [Recommended solution: Remove and re-add Zoom meeting in team calendar](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3033.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### Zoom Link Access Issues\n\n  - [George Haikal experienced repeated difficulties accessing the meeting](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2879.0)\n  - [Link worked for some participants but not for George](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2908.0)\n  - [Multiple attempts to join via calendar invite were unsuccessful](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2889.0)\n  - [Confusion about whether the issue was calendar-related or Zoom-specific](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2917.0)\n\n### Troubleshooting Steps\n\n  - [Checked calendar invite multiple times](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2884.0)\n  - [Reviewed Zoom video instructions](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2917.0)\n  - Examined meeting host details (<team@growthxlabs.com>)\n  - [Requested direct link paste from other participants](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2957.0)\n\n### Root Cause Analysis\n\n  - [Suspected issue with calendar integration or Zoom account settings](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=2889.0)\n  - [Focus shifted to team profile and calendar management](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3128.0)\n\n### Proposed Solution\n\n  - [Remove Zoom meeting from existing calendar invite](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3093.0)\n  - [Access team Zoomer account to adjust settings](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3074.0)\n  - [Re-add new Zoom meeting to calendar invite](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3095.0)\n  - [Ensure proper sharing settings for all participants](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3112.0)\n\n### Team Profile Navigation\n\n  - [Guided navigation to team profile section](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3076.0)\n  - [Accessed calendar settings within team profile](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3079.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [Edit existing meeting in team calendar](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3093.0)\n  - [Remove current Zoom meeting link](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3095.0)\n  - [Add new Zoom meeting with correct settings](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3095.0)\n  - [Share updated invite with all participants](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3105.0)\n  - [Verify upcoming meetings show correctly in team calendar](https://fathom.video/share/-gr3TBSaiDeVxyYsHu2FxqushyU8hNPi?tab=summary&timestamp=3118.0)\n  - [Monitor future meetings to ensure resolution of access issue